      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is super hard to reach and i hate waiting for calls. i only take like one pill every once in a while when it's really bad, not like all the time. is it really that dangerous for just a single dose? it's just a standard headache so i don't think it'll do much damage.",
